  <brief_title>Efficacy of HIFU-AR on Blood Loss Reduction in Patients With Liver Metastases Requiring Hepatectomy</brief_title>
  <acronym>HIFU-AR</acronym>
  <official_title>Randomized, Open-label, Phase II Study to Evaluate the Efficacy of High-Intensity Focused Ultrasound Assisted Hepatic Resection (HIFU-AR) on Blood Loss Reduction in Patients With Liver Metastases Requiring Hepatectomy</official_title>
