  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate whether HIFU-assisted liver resection (HIFU-AR)
      results in reduced blood loss compared to standard liver resection in patients with LM.This
      is a prospective, monocentric, randomized (1:1 ratio), comparative, open-label Phase II
      study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
